Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:50.46,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\fax-0.05}你是否还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:55.63,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\fax-0.05}在由心发出呐喊时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.09,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\fax-0.05}想再看一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:20:00.14,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\fax-0.05}那片天空
