Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:30.73,OP3_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\fax-0.05}君の瞳は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:36.15,OP3_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\fax-0.05}光輝いて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:39.49,OP3_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\fax-0.05}僕の瞳に
